description: The first impression I got from Cole is that she is sassy and needs to be in control. Nothing wrong with that of course, but as she quickly found out, it's hard to remain in control when getting fucked hard and fast by our machines. I'll let you be the judge of what happened next, did she squirt, or did her bladder simply let go? Before the shoot was due to be over she was so thouroughly fucked out she simply could not go on, she couldn't even talk any more. We'll need to get her back for round 2.
title: Cole Conners
